{"tid":1658910,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"南亞人係香港民族既一部份","createTime":"2019-10-16T16:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T16:18:24.000Z","uid":285165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1fb65283d1cbdeb93220f0d8cf993072107a60","tid":1658910,"uid":285165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:17:50.000Z","msg":"東方日報 梁美芬 <br />\n成日label南亞人係難民 同 治安問題<br />\n點解呀? <br />\n因為佢地想用支那人沖淡我地香港特色<br />\n香港就係國際城市 唔止係得黃種人<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">冇南亞人既香港唔係香港</span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢地都係受壓縮既一群 <br />\n香港教育制度之下 <br />\n有冇專for既地既中文教材同配套?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而支援支那人既教育政策就大把<br />\n<br />\n連登仔 都中左一次James伏 比人話種族歧視<br />\n就唔好再中la<br />\n<br />\n南亞人係手足 係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打人既只係黑社會 <br />\n<br />\n咪比黑警有藉口扮我地搞南亞人鋪頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da9c8471fd61cb2411e3a0b0b64327bb8630abe","tid":1658910,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}